cs.DM, cs.CC, cs.LO, cs.SY, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is the most likely category as reaction systems are discrete dynamical systems and the paper deals with decision problems related to their dynamics.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper provides the computational complexity of the decision problems.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses logical formalisms to describe the behavior of reaction systems.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with the dynamics of bio-chemical systems.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the use of reaction systems as a computational model for bio-chemical phenomena, which could be relevant to AI applications.
